              {
                "lang_tag": "ui7_zigbee_devwiz_reset_intro",
                "text": "The Vera Controller will now begin to reset this device."
              },
              {
                "lang_tag": "ui7_kitdevice_2991_step_6_02",
                "text": "To reset the device:\n<br>\n1. Press the hidden button between the HOLD and FAN buttons.<br>\n2. While pressing the hidden button use your other finger and slide from (+) to (-) located on the right side of the screen. '01' will be displayed in the middle.<br>\n3. In programming mode, navigate to menu option 13, press HOLD to enter the 'Leave Network' menu, press HOLD again to display '01' then navigate to 11 and press HOLD one more time to confirm.<br>\nThis will allow the thermostat to be added to the unit successfully."
              }
            ]
